								id="name" class="requiredInfo" value='${paraMap.name}'
								placeholder="이름" /> <br> <!-- <span id="error" class="error">닉네임은 필수 사항 입니다.</span> -->
								<span class="CheckResult" id="nameCheckResult"></span>
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<td class="tiles">
